'''麥可·蓋瑞·佛提奈維奇'''（{{lang-en|Michael Gary Foltynewicz}}，{{IPAc-en|f|oʊ|l|t|ᵻ|ˈ|n|ɛ|v|ᵻ|tʃ}}，<ref name=bowmantrade>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Braves send Gattis to Astros for 3 prospects|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/106406948/braves-send-evan-gattis-to-astros-for-mike-foltynewicz-andrew-thurman-rio-ruiz|access-date=January 22, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=January 14, 2015}}</ref>{{bd|1991年|10月7日|}}），綽號「Folty」，為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前為自由球員。他先前曾效力過太空人、勇士與遊騎兵等隊。

[[2010年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2010年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，太空人在第一輪選進佛提奈維奇。他在2015年被交易到勇士隊，後來在2020年被勇士隊指定讓渡。
==職業生涯==
===休士頓太空人===
[[File:Mike_Foltynewicz_signs_autographs_in_Jan_2014.jpg|250px]]
太空人在2010年選秀會上於首輪19順位選進佛提奈維奇。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Helfgot|first1=Mike|title=Minooka's Foltynewicz picked 19th by Astros|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2010-06-07/sports/ct-spt-0608-prep-mlb-draft-foltynewic20100607_1_major-league-baseball-draft-picked-mike-foltynewicz|access-date=May 2, 2016|work=Chicago Tribune|date=June 7, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=McTaggart|first1=Brian|title=Astros nab hard-throwing righty at No. 19|url=http://m.astros.mlb.com/news/article/10921346|access-date=May 2, 2016|work=MLB.com|date=June 8, 2010}}</ref>他原本打算繼續攻讀大學，不過最後仍選擇和球隊簽約。<ref name=Helfgot>{{cite news|last=Helfgot|first=Mike|title=2010 Chicago Tribune baseball All-State first team: Minooka's Mike Foltynewicz|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2010-06-18/sports/chi-prep-base-all-state-foltynewicz_1_all-state-chicago-tribune-houston-astros|access-date=January 26, 2014|newspaper=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=June 18, 2010}}</ref>該年他從新人聯盟出發，隔年升上1A。<ref name=autogenerated1>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=foltyn001mic Mike Foltynewicz Minor Leagues Statistics & History | Baseball-Reference.com<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

2012年，他在1A投出14勝4敗，防禦率3.14的成績。<ref>{{cite news|title=Astros name Minor League Player, Pitcher of the Year|url=http://m.astros.mlb.com/news/article/38742406|access-date=May 2, 2016|work=MLB.com|date=September 20, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Pitcher Mike Foltynewicz ready to soar in Astros' system|url=https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-14234105CC08CF80.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911075827/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-14234105CC08CF80.html|archive-date=September 11, 2016|access-date=May 2, 2016|work=Herald News|via=Highbeam Research|date=October 28, 2012}}</ref>他也獲得升上2A的機會，後來他拿下5勝3敗，防禦率為2.87。<ref name=BRM>{{cite web|title=Michael Foltynewicz Minor League Statistics & History|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=foltyn001mic|website=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=August 3, 2014}}</ref>

[[File:Mike_Foltynewicz_pitches_in_August_2014_MMP.jpg|250px]]
2014年8月2日，在3A拿下7勝7敗的佛提奈維奇升上大聯盟。<ref name=McTaggart>{{cite web|last1=McTaggart|first1=Brian|title=Astros call up hard-throwing righty Foltynewicz|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/hou/astros-call-up-hard-throwing-right-hander-mike-foltynewiczymd=20140801&content_id=87434104&vkey=news_hou|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|access-date=August 3, 2014|date=August 1, 2014}}</ref>不過這年他吞下1敗，防禦率為5.30。<ref name=BRM/>
===亞特蘭大勇士===
2015年1月14日，太空人用佛提奈維奇、Andrew Thurman及Rio Ruiz等球員向勇士隊交易Evan Gattis跟James Hoyt。<ref name=bowmantrade/><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/12167911/evan-gattis-traded-houston-astros-atlanta-braves |title=Braves trade Evan Gattis to Astros |date=January 14, 2015 |access-date=January 15, 2015 |publisher=ESPN |others=ESPN.com news services}}</ref>佛提奈維奇開季先待在3A，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Braves option No. 2 prospect Foltynewicz to Triple-A|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/116400450/braves-option-no-2-prospect-mike-foltynewicz-to-triple-a|access-date=April 5, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=April 4, 2015}}</ref>後來因為Chris Johnson受傷而成功登上大聯盟。表現不佳的[[崔佛·卡希爾|崔佛·卡希爾]]也被佛提奈維奇取代其位置。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cunningham|first1=Michael|title=Braves' Fredi G. says Cahill move to bullpen 'not permanent'|url=http://www.ajc.com/news/sports/baseball/braves-fredi-g-says-cahill-move-to-bullpen-not-per/nk6pb/|access-date=September 22, 2015|work=Atlanta Journal Constitution|date=April 30, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Braves turn to Foltynewicz for tonight's start|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/121373508/braves-tab-prospect-mike-foltynewicz-for-tonights-start-vs-reds|access-date=September 22, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=April 30, 2015}}</ref>他在勇士隊的初登場便奪下勝投，而且還敲出大聯盟首安。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Henry|first1=George|title=Foltynewicz wins 1st career start as Atlanta Braves beat Cincinnati Reds, 4–3|url=http://www.gainesvilletimes.com/archives/109474/|work=Gainesville Times|agency=Associated Press|date=May 1, 2015}}{{Dead link|date=April 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>後來他因為防禦率偏高而遭到下放，<ref>{{cite news|title=Mike Foltynewicz optioned to Triple-A|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/13102432/atlanta-braves-option-rhp-mike-foltynewicz-triple-gwinnett|access-date=September 22, 2015|agency=Associated Press|work=ESPN.com|date=June 17, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Collazo|first1=Carlos|title=Braves option Foltynewicz, call up Castro|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/131243338/braves-option-right-hander-mike-foltynewicz|access-date=September 22, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=June 18, 2015}}</ref>不過隨著Joey Terdoslavich也被下放，佛提奈維奇成功重返大聯盟。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Foltynewicz rejoins Braves in relief role|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/135267580/foltynewicz-recalled-to-join-braves-bullpen|access-date=September 22, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=July 7, 2015}}</ref>8月中旬，佛提奈維奇表現開始下滑。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Foltynewicz patient in recovery from blood clot|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/163392834/mike-foltynewicz-recovers-from-blood-clot|access-date=February 2, 2016|work=MLB.com|date=February 1, 2016}}</ref>後來他在9月份確診罹患軟骨炎，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Foltynewicz placed on DL; Perez starts Wednesday|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/146818996/braves-place-mike-foltynewicz-on-disabled-list|access-date=September 20, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=September 1, 2015}}</ref>到後來甚至發展成肺炎。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mark|first1=Bowman|title=Folty recovering, hopes to pitch again soon|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/148538142/mike-foltynewicz-recovering-from-pneumonia|access-date=September 20, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=September 10, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Pneumonia likely to limit Foltynewicz to bullpen|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/149747326|access-date=September 20, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=September 15, 2015}}</ref>最後他動了肋骨切除手術，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Foltynewicz has surgery to alleviate clots|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/150862594/mike-foltynewicz-has-surgery-to-reduce-clots|access-date=September 22, 2015|work=MLB.com|date=September 21, 2015}}</ref>並因為瘦了約9.1公斤。<ref>{{cite news|title=Braves' Foltynewicz continues recovery from blood clots|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=14692698|access-date=February 2, 2016|agency=Associated Press|work=ESPN.com|date=February 1, 2016}}</ref>2015年，他拿下4勝6敗，防禦率5.71。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Odum |first1=Charles |title=Braves' Foltynewicz continues recovery from blood clots |url=http://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/sdut-braves-foltynewicz-continues-recovery-from-blood-2016feb01-story.html |access-date=September 14, 2018 |work=San Diego Union Tribune |agency=Associated Press |date=February 1, 2016}}</ref>

2016年，球團為了讓他養傷而將他暫時下放小聯盟。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Foltynewicz optioned to Triple-A Gwinnett|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/169734644/braves-send-mike-foltynewicz-to-triple-a|access-date=March 30, 2016|work=MLB.com|date=March 30, 2016}}</ref>不過這年勇士隊的投手群可說是傷兵滿營，使得他在6月底必須歸隊支援先發。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Staff woes force Braves to hasten Folty's return|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/186954328/mike-foltynewicz-to-return-to-braves-thursday|access-date=June 30, 2016|work=MLB.com|date=June 29, 2016}}</ref>

2017年6月30日，佛提奈維奇投了8局無安打，可惜在第9局被敲出全壘打。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Tafur|first1=Vic|title=Matt Olson's homer ends Mike Foltynewicz's no-hit bid in 9th|url=http://www.sfgate.com/athletics/article/Olson-HR-ends-Braves-no-hit-bid-in-ninth-11260540.php|access-date=November 24, 2017|work=San Francisco Chronicle|date=June 30, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=O'Brien|first1=David|title=Foltynewicz's no-hit bid ends in 9th inning vs. A's|url=http://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/foltynewicz-hit-bid-ends-9th-inning/BbWy4L5DMgv4VqoxRYjIQL/|access-date=November 24, 2017|work=Atlanta Journal-Constitution|date=July 1, 2017}}</ref>這年他拿下10勝13敗，防禦率4.79。<ref name="aparb">{{cite news|title=Pitchers Mike Foltynewicz, Kendall Graveman lose in arbitration; players lead 7–6|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/22393997/pitchers-mike-foltynewicz-kendall-graveman-lose-arbitration-players-lead-7-6|access-date=February 11, 2018|agency=Associated Press|work=ESPN.com|date=February 10, 2018}}</ref>

2018年6月1日，佛提奈維奇拿下生涯首場完投完封勝。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Folty does Maddux impression as Braves top DC |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mike-foltynewicz-throws-shutout-vs-nationals/c-279383564 |access-date=September 14, 2018 |work=MLB.com |date=June 2, 2018}}</ref>他在上半季以6勝5敗入選明星賽。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hill |first1=Jordan D. |title=The Braves have the most players on the NL All-Star team. See who made the squad. |url=https://www.ledger-enquirer.com/sports/mlb/atlanta-braves/article214550540.html |access-date=September 14, 2018 |work=Ledger Enquirer |date=July 9, 2018}}</ref>[[2018年國家聯盟分區賽|2018年國家聯盟分區賽]]，佛提奈維奇擔任首場先發，不過他僅投2局便失4分吞敗。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sanchez |first1=Jesse |title=Folty ready for redemption after brief G1 start |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mike-foltynewicz-labors-in-game-1-of-nlds/c-297097184 |access-date=October 8, 2018 |work=MLB.com |date=October 5, 2018}}</ref>

2019年，他與球隊簽下1年547萬5000美元的合約。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Braves avoid arbitration with Folty, 6 others |url=https://www.mlb.com/braves/news/mike-foltynewicz-avoids-arbitration-in-2019/c-302611380 |access-date=January 14, 2019 |date=January 11, 2019}}</ref>由於手肘受傷，他無法擔任勇士隊的開幕戰先發。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Folty scratched from start with elbow issue |url=https://www.mlb.com/braves/news/mike-foltynewicz-scratched-injury-spring-training |access-date=April 7, 2019 |work=MLB.com |date=February 28, 2019}}</ref>[2019年國家聯盟分區賽]]，雖然他贏得第二戰，<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Resilient Folty repays Braves' trust with G2 gem |url=https://www.mlb.com/braves/news/foltynewicz-strikes-out-seven-in-nlds-win |access-date=January 11, 2020 |work=MLB.com |date=October 6, 2019}}</ref>卻在第五戰大崩盤，讓勇士隊提前被淘汰。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tucker |first1=Tim |title=Mike Foltynewicz 'very embarrassed' by Game 5 performance |url=https://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/after-game-gem-foltynewicz-lasts-just-pitches-game/LSI4gyTKYtFLQGjTxJWrUM/ |access-date=January 11, 2020 |work=Atlanta Journal Constitution |date=October 9, 2019}}</ref>

2020年，他與球隊簽下1年642萬5000美元的合約。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Folty, Dansby among 6 Braves to agree to deals |url=https://www.mlb.com/braves/news/braves-2020-arbitration-roundup |access-date=January 11, 2020 |work=MLB.com |date=January 10, 2020}}</ref>然而他在該年球季的第一場先發只投了3局便狂失6分，最後也被球隊揮棄。他在7月30日被球隊釋出，<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Foltynewicz outrighted after clearing waivers |url=https://www.mlb.com/braves/news/mike-foltynewicz-clears-waivers |access-date=July 30, 2020 |work=MLB.com |date=July 30, 2020}}</ref>11月2日投入自由市場。<ref>{{cite news |title=https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/mlb/mike-foltynewicz-among-several-former-major-leaguers-to-become-free-agents/ar-BB1aD5Y5 |url=https://www.ajc.com/sports/atlanta-braves/is-mike-foltynewicz-a-free-agent/SMGBX7KH4JHLBGN4KGCCCYKJZY/ |access-date=November 7, 2020 |work=Atlanta Journal Constitution |date=October 27, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Free agency granted to 422 minor leaguers, including Braves' Mike Foltynewicz |url=https://www.mdjonline.com/sports/free-agency-granted-to-422-minor-leaguers-including-braves-mike-foltynewicz/article_a36961dc-0c18-5eff-959b-dbb18596e76f.html |access-date=November 7, 2020 |work=Marietta Daily Journal |date=November 2, 2020}}</ref>
===德州遊騎兵===
2021年2月10日，他和遊騎兵隊簽下1年200萬美元的合約。<ref>https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/30874277/rangers-sign-former-nl-all-star-rhp-mike-foltynewicz-1-year-deal</ref>

==個人生活==
佛提奈維奇目前已婚，<ref name="MLB.com">{{Cite news |url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/262240952/braves-mike-foltynewicz-spreads-joy-to-kids/ |title=Community-minded Folty lights up young faces |last=Bowman |first=Mark |date=November 22, 2017 |access-date=November 24, 2017 |work=MLB.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Cooper|first1=Jon|title=Braves get in spirit with tree lighting ceremony|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/262764814/braves-host-first-tree-lighting-ceremony|access-date=December 3, 2017|work=MLB.com|date=December 2, 2017}}</ref>2018年其長子出生。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Foltynewicz strolls back into camp a proud papa|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mike-foltynewicz-back-with-braves-as-father/c-266380392|access-date=February 14, 2018|work=MLB.com|date=February 13, 2018}}</ref>
